The paper deals with processing cybersecurity-related information from Twitter using deep neural networks. This involves natural language processing (NLP) tasks such as text classification and named entity recognition. Therefore, cs.CL (Computation and Language) is the most likely sub-category. The paper also deals with cybersecurity, which falls under cs.CR (Cryptography and Security) and cs.SI (Social and Information Networks). The use of deep neural networks for processing the information also falls under cs.LG (Machine Learning) and cs.IR (Information Retrieval).
